trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element that specifies settings for an instance of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"></xref> for hosting workflow-based [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en konfigurasjonselementet som angir innstillingene for en forekomst av <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"> </xref> vert basert på arbeidsflyt for [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.

trans-unit.source: To enable or disable one of the `ServiceDebugElement` features using a configuration file, you must: 1.
trans-unit.target: Aktivere eller deaktivere en av de `ServiceDebugElement` funksjoner ved hjelp av en konfigurasjonsfil, må du: 1.

trans-unit.source: Add a behavior configuration attribute to the service element of your [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service.
trans-unit.target: Legg til en virkemåte konfigurasjonsattributtet tjenesteelementet i din [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Endpoint behaviors are configured on `endpoint` elements; service behaviors are configured on `service` elements.
trans-unit.target: Endepunktet virkemåter er konfigurert på `endpoint` elementer; tjenesten virkemåter er konfigurert på `service` elementer.

trans-unit.source: Create a `serviceBehaviors` section, and add a behavior element with the name that corresponds to the `behaviorConfiguration` attribute value from step 1.
trans-unit.target: Opprett en `serviceBehaviors` delen, og Legg til en virkemåte elementet med navn som samsvarer med den `behaviorConfiguration` attributtverdien fra trinn 1.

trans-unit.source: Add a `serviceDebug` element to the behavior element from step 2, and enable or disable the various properties as needed.
trans-unit.target: Legg til en `serviceDebug` elementet som elementet virkemåte fra trinn 2, og aktivere eller deaktivere forskjellige egenskaper etter behov.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of this behavior element.
trans-unit.target: Henter elementtypen dette problemet.

trans-unit.source: The type of the behavior.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags virkemåten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the time that a cached instance will expire.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir hvor lenge en bufret forekomst utløper.

trans-unit.source: The time that a cached instance will expire.
trans-unit.target: Tidspunktet en bufret forekomst utløper.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of common parameters used by services.
trans-unit.target: Henter samling av vanlige parametere som brukes av tjenester.

trans-unit.source: This collection will typically include the database connection string that might be shared by durable services.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen inneholder vanligvis database-tilkoblingsstreng som kan deles av robust services.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_NameValueConfigurationCollection" name="NameValueConfigurationCollection" href=""></xref> that contains common parameters used by services.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_NameValueConfigurationCollection" name="NameValueConfigurationCollection" href=""> </xref> som inneholder vanlige parametere som brukes av tjenester.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a custom behavior based on the settings of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en egendefinert virkemåte basert på innstillingene for dette konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: A custom behavior based on the settings of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: En egendefinert virkemåte basert på innstillingene for dette konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether performance counters are enabled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om-ytelsestellere er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: Performance counters provide information on various workflow-related statistics, but they cause a performance penalty when the workflow runtime engine starts, and when workflow instances are running.
trans-unit.target: Ytelsestellere gir informasjon om ulike arbeidsflyt-relaterte statistikk, men de forårsaker en innvirkning på ytelsen når arbeidsflyten runtime engine startes, og når arbeidsflytforekomster kjører.

trans-unit.source: The default value is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if performance counters are enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis-ytelsestellere er aktivert. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på arbeidsflyt runtime motoren.

trans-unit.source: This property is used to set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.Name%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes til å angi <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.Name%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom streng.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på arbeidsflyt runtime motoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"></xref> instance that contains a collection of <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"></xref> objects that can be attributes or <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"></xref> objects of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"> </xref> -forekomst som inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"> </xref> objekter som kan være attributter eller <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"> </xref> objekter av denne konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.NetTcpContextBindingElement.ContextProtectionLevel%2A> property is also contained in this property collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.NetTcpContextBindingElement.ContextProtectionLevel%2A>egenskapen finnes også i denne egenskapsutvalg.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.NetTcpContextBindingElement.ContextProtectionLevel%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"></xref> instance that contains a collection of <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"></xref> objects that can be attributes or <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"></xref> objects of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"> </xref> -forekomst som inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"> </xref> objekter som kan være attributter eller <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"> </xref> objekter av denne konfigurasjonselementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of services that will be added to the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"></xref> engine.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av tjenestene som legges til i <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"> </xref> motoren.

trans-unit.source: The services specified in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection> will be initialized by the workflow runtime engine and added to its services when the appropriate <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> constructor is called.
trans-unit.target: Tjenestene som er angitt i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection>blir initialisert av arbeidsflyten runtime motoren og legges til tjenestene når den riktige <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime>konstruktøren kalles.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the services specified in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection> must follow certain rules about the signatures of their constructors.
trans-unit.target: Derfor tjenestene som er angitt i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection>må følge regler om signaturer av deres konstruktører.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement>

trans-unit.source: The collection of services that will be added to the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"></xref> engine.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av tjenestene som legges til i <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime"> </xref> motoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether validation will occur on creation of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om valideringen gjennomføres ved oppretting av arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to `true`, the workflow validation is executed every time <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen er satt til `true`, arbeidsflyt-valideringen utføres hver gang <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A>kalles.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A>

trans-unit.source: If validation errors are found, a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowValidationFailedException> error is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes valideringsfeilene, en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowValidationFailedException>feil har oppstått.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowValidationFailedException>

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to `false`, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A> creates a workflow instance and skips validation.
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen er satt til `false`, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A>oppretter en arbeidsflytforekomst og hopper over valideringen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow%2A>

trans-unit.source: In this case, the host application must ensure that the workflow is properly configured, or the runtime error occurs.
trans-unit.target: Vertsprogrammet må i så fall Kontroller at arbeidsflyten er riktig konfigurert, eller runtime feilen forekommer.

trans-unit.source: The default value for this property is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien for denne egenskapen er `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if validation will occur on creation; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis validering forekommer på oppretting; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
